items.description: external unit used in many heat pumps of the Altherma series. This model has sufficient power for hot water supply and heating of rooms with an area of ​​40 square meters. m. The heart of the unit is an airtight inverter compressor with an oscillating rotor. The inverter power management method and a number of technical solutions ensure minimum consumption of the air conditioning system. Maximum energy efficiency ensures minimum energy consumption by systems that use this device with an energy efficiency class up to A+++. The new outdoor unit of the ERGA-EV series now comes standard with a new side cover which has two advantages: Improved protection of cable and pipe connections. A more aesthetic appearance of the heat pump. Daikin engineers have confirmed that this heat pump works reliably in heating mode down to -25 C, allowing owners to heat their homes very economically during many cold periods in this climate zone. The device's compactness and light weight make it easy to install. The installation uses R32 freon, which significantly reduces the impact on the environment (compared to R-410A freon) and increases the energy efficiency of the system. Type - Altherma outdoor unit Compressor type - Rotary Power in cooling mode, kW 4.86 (1) / 4.52 (2) Power in heating mode, kW 4.3 (1) / 4.2 (2) Energy consumption in cooling mode, kW 0.81 (1) / 1.36 (2) Energy consumption in heating mode, kW 0.84 (1) / 1.26 (2) Heating energy efficiency class A+++ Dimensions of the outdoor unit (WxHxD), mm 740x884x388 Weight of the outdoor unit, kg 58.5 Operating temperature range in cooling mode +10/+43 Operating temperature range in heating mode -25/+25 Lower temperature limit for heating operation -25 Sound pressure level of the outdoor unit (cooling), dBA 48 Sound pressure level of the external unit (heating), dBA 44 Refrigerant type R-32 Power supply ~1/230/50

items.itemName: EHVH04S18E6V Indoor floor unit with Daikin heat pump
items.description: indoor floor unit with an air-to-water heat pump, including a hot water tank, provides efficient heating and hot water for rooms up to 40 square meters. m, with a thermal capacity of 4 kW, is ideal for low-energy houses. The volume of the tank is 180 liters. The system can be installed in new construction projects and is the most effective alternative to traditional boilers. Features of the floor unit Daikin EHVH04S18E6V: The model is compatible with external units of the ERGA04 series. The 80 liter stainless steel hot water tank is combined with a heat pump, making it easy to install. For easy access, the manufacturer placed the circuit board and hydraulic components at the front. Due to its small dimensions, the unit takes up little space. Daikin EHVH04S18E6V has a built-in backup heater with a capacity of 2-4-6 kW. Ability to control the heat pump by voice. Even with a remote control or control app, your hands can be busy. Thanks to modern intelligent technologies, you can control the air conditioner using your voice. The Daikin Residential Controller program will simplify the use of this unit. items.description: Daikin Alterma indoor unit, reversible with an air-water heat pump. Ideal for rooms with low energy consumption. The productivity of this system is enough to provide hot water for a small family and maintain a comfortable temperature in the room. Thanks to the "Online controller" function, you will be able to control the unit from any convenient place through a smartphone, laptop, PC, tablet. For easy access, the manufacturer placed the printed circuit board in front. There are also hydraulic components. The Daikin Residential Controller function allows you to control the microclimate in the room using a phone or tablet. The interactive thermostat allows you to control the temperature, operating mode and time for each room. Compact dimensions allow this model to be installed in places with little space, as there is practically no need for side gaps. The modern design of the device is perfectly combined with other household appliances. Ability to control voice. Combination with stainless steel tank or ECH2O heat accumulator. Type - Reversible indoor unit Color - White + Black Material - Polymer, sheet metal Dimensions (WxHxD), mm 440x840x390 Weight, kg 42 Heater power, kW 52 Maximum water temperature in the tank +65 Maximum water pressure in the tank, bar 3 Protection against corrosion - Yes Noise level (nom.), dBA - 28 Power supply ~1/230/50

items.itemName: EHBH08E6V/ERGA06EVH Daikin Altherma series wall indoor unit
items.description:
Daikin Altherma 3 R W series wall-mounted indoor unit for air-to-water heat pump heating, which will be an ideal choice for low-energy houses. This model, in combination with an external unit, is able to maintain an optimal microclimate in rooms with an area of ​​up to 60-75 square meters, having a heat productivity index of 6-7.5 kW. The extended mode of operation for heating up to -25 and the minimum noise level makes the Daikin Alterma heat pump an excellent choice. Features of Daikin EHBH08E6V Manufacturer Daikin for simplified access to boards and hydraulic components placed them at the front. The compact unit with dimensions (440x840x390 mm) practically does not require side clearances, as it has a small installation area. An ECH2O thermal accumulator or a stainless steel tank can be combined with a heat pump. The simple modern design of the indoor unit harmoniously fits into most modern interiors. The temperature range of operation has been increased to -25 degrees. The Daikin Residential Controller app now offers voice control for even greater comfort and ease for users. This handy feature frees up your hands by reducing the number of clicks and making block management faster than ever before. Type: Wall unit Color - White + Black Material - Polymer/sheet metal Dimensions (WxHxD), mm - 440x840x390

Weight, kg 42 Heater power, kW 4 Operating range of heating, water side +15~+65 Operating range of hot water heating, water side +25~+75 Noise level (nom.), dBA 28 Power supply ~1/230/50

items.description: Multi split system Daikin FTXM35A Perfera (indoor unit). The internal wall unit of the Daikin multi-split system model FTXM35A from the Perfera series is suitable for a room up to 40 m2. Laconic design, modern technologies, the number one manufacturer of air conditioning in the world - all this makes this model quite promising to choose. Characteristics and functions: Two-zone motion sensor (directs the flow to the area of the room where there are no people to avoid unpleasant sensations, and when the room is empty - includes energy saving mode) Wi-Fi, air conditioning control through the Onecta app Adjustment of blinds (horizontal and vertical) Auto mode: the system selects modes (cold or warm) for maximum comfort Timer Modern plasma filtration (Flash Streamer): starting chemical reactions with particles that pollute the air, breaking down allergens, eliminating odors Voice control of the main functions (Amazon Alexa or Google Assistant) Even distribution of air, even in the farthest corners of the room - guaranteed clean cold/warm air

Features and functions: Dual-zone motion sensor (directs the flow to the area of the room where there are no people to avoid unpleasant sensations, and when the room is empty - includes energy saving mode)
Wi-Fi, air conditioning control via the Onecta app
Adjusting blinds (horizontal and vertical)
Auto mode: the system selects modes (cold or warm) for maximum comfort
Timer
Modern plasma filtration (Flash Streamer): starting chemical reactions with particles that pollute the air, breaking down allergens, destroying odors
Voice control of basic functions (Amazon Alexa or Google Assistant)
Even distribution of air, even in the farthest corners of the room - clean cold/warm air is guaranteed

items.itemName: Gasoline generator P6500AP Atlas Copco 5 -5.5 kW
items.description:
P6500AP Atlas Copco gasoline generator is 25% quieter than cheaper Chinese models, premium quality
Time of main continuous operation - 24 h/d P 6500 AP S5 50Hz 230V With autostart
Nominal power -kW - 5
Number of phases - Single-phase maximum power - 5.5 kW
The generator has an enlarged fuel tank with a capacity of 25 l.

The engine is started by an electric starter from the key.

AVR system (automatic voltage regulation) — stable voltage under any load.

Sound-insulating housing, noise level of only 72dB(A) at 7m — comfortable use even near residential areas

Fuel indicator, hour meter, voltmeter, protection against low oil level and overheating — full control over the generator.

Availability of connectors and cables for parallel operation - expand the system as needed.

There are two types of sockets, a fuel indicator, an engine hour meter and a voltmeter. - enlarged fuel tank - oil level sensor - overheating protection - complies with EU noise standards (sound insulation casing) - sockets - automatic voltage regulation system (AVR) - Indicators: low engine oil level, engine overload - connectors and cables for parallel operation
Gasoline single-phase generator P6500 Atlas Copco Designed for intensive daily use. The generator is copper wound and gives excellent performance combined with ease of use and transport thanks to the wheels. The handle and wheels can be assembled by any user. The unit allows you to have electricity where it is needed and meets EU noise standards. The generator has an enlarged fuel tank with a capacity of 25 liters. Equipped with an AVR board that provides automatic regulation of the output voltage, making it always perfectly constant under different load conditions. The engine is started by an electric starter from the key. It has a differential switch and an undervoltage control relay in its arsenal. Protection against operation with low oil level is installed. The sound pressure level (LPA) at a distance of 7 m is only 72 dB(A) - for comparison: Chinese generators of small power (eg 3 kW) produce a noise level of at least 92 dB, which is 25% noisier than a Swedish one! Which ensures convenient operation of both the generator and the surrounding people.

items.description: This Easy Altivar 610 drive is a frequency converter for three-phase asynchronous motors. It operates at a rated supply voltage of 380V to 415V AC. It is suitable for motors rated up to 22 kW / 30 hp for applications requiring light overload (up to 120%). It is suitable for motors rated up to 18.5 kW / 25 hp for applications requiring significant overload (up to 150%). It offers a plug-and-play solution where parameters are pre-set at the factory to the desired configuration to help save time on setup and operation. It has built-in RF interference filters in accordance with the electromagnetic compatibility standard for variable speed drives IEC/EN 61800-3, edition 2, category C3 in environment 1 or 2. It weighs 13.9 kg and its dimensions are: 211 mm wide, 495 mm high, 232 mm deep. This actuator has been specifically designed for standard applications in the water and wastewater, oil and gas, process, machine and building control market segments.

items.description: Communication board Siemens CB 1241 - 6ES7241-1CH30-1XB0. items.itemName: 6ES7332-5HF00-0AB0 SIMATIC S7-300 ANALOG SIGNALS OUTPUT MODULE
items.description: The Siemens 6ES7332-5HF00-0AB0 module is a SIMATIC S7-300 digital input/output module. It is designed to be connected to a SIMATIC S7-300 controller and provides the ability to connect digital I/O signals. Features of the module: 1. Number of digital inputs: 16 2. Number of digital outputs: 16 3. Type of inputs: 24 V DC 4. Type of outputs: 24 V DC, 0.5 A 5. Protection against overload and short circuit on the outputs 6. Compatibility with SIMATIC S7-300 controllers The module has a compact size and can be easily installed in the bus on the back of the controller. It is intended for use in industrial automated systems such as production lines, material handling, etc.

items.description:
SIMATIC S7-300, 20-pole front connector for signal modules, terminals with screw clamps. The initial element is simple and convenient for connecting sensors and actuators of external input and output circuits. It has a protective cover that closes when the module is connected. In addition, replacement of modules does not require dismantling of external connectors. The connector has many functions and capabilities.
The modular design of the S7-300 controller provides for operation with natural cooling, and also provides the possibility of obtaining optimal solutions for building systems for automatic control of technological processes in various areas of industrial production.
The Siemens 6ES7392-1AJ00-0AA0 connector is resistant to contamination and temperature fluctuations, durable, designed for long-term use. Meets all norms and standards of European quality. The number of poles is 20

Operating temperature - 0...60°C

items.description:
3RT2025-1AP00 Contactor (magnetic starter) of the Sirius system, with a current of up to 17 A, for switching motors with a power of up to 7.5 kW (at 400 V) or resistive loads up to 40 A
The Siemens Sirius 3RT2025-1AP00 contactor is designed for switching power circuits when starting electric motors with a capacity of up to 7.5 kW (at 400 V), as well as for switching on/off without inductive loads (category AC - 1) with currents up to 40 A
The magnetic starter 3RT2025-1AP00 is used under standard conditions, in closed rooms, in general industrial and administrative and economic spheres, both separately and as part of the Sirius modular system for switching, starting and protecting electric motors, as well as for switching low-inductive (non-inductive) loads
The Siemens 3RT2025-1AP00 magnetic starter has the following performance:
- standard execution
- with an alternating current coil with a frequency of 50 Hz
- for mounting on a vertical surface or DIN rail

items.description:
The SIRIUS surge arrester 3RT2916-1DG00 from Siemens operates with a noise-suppressing diode within the voltage range of 12-250 VDC. This makes the 3RT2916-1DG00 surge arrester an ideal solution for surge suppression on size S00 contactor relays and power contactors.
Typical applications include motor and plant control, lighting control switching and signal multiplication.
Limiter 3RT2916-1DG00 from Siemens meets the standards set by European quality and safety standards. Moreover, it is characterized by high accuracy and speed of response in case of overload or overvoltage.

items.description: Acti9 iC60N is a low-voltage circuit breaker (CB). It is a single-pole circuit breaker with a rated current of 2A and a tripping curve of C. The rated short-circuit breaking capacity is 50 kA at 220 to 240 V AC according to IEC 60947-2 and 6000 A at 230 V AC according to IEC 60898-1. The automatic circuit breaker protects the electrical circuit from short-circuit and overload shocks. VisiTrip's mechanical indicator signals when the circuit breaker has tripped, thus reducing the time it takes to identify a problem and resolve it. The green VisiSafe strip ensures that the contacts are physically opened, allowing for safe maintenance. The mechanism of instant activation increases the service life. It has an electrical wear resistance of up to 10,000 cycles and a mechanical wear resistance of up to 20,000 cycles. The nominal insulation voltage Ui is 500 V AC. Its limitation class is 3 (according to МЕК60898-1). Designed for installation on a DIN rail. Its width is 2 modules of 9 mm. Degree of contamination of the device 3. Overvoltage category IV. The color of the product is white (RAL9003). Dimensions: (W) 18mm x (H) 85mm x (D) 78.5mm. Weight 0.215 kg. According to the MEK 60529 standard, the degree of protection is IP20 and IP40 when installed in a panel. Operating temperature from -35°C to 70°C. Storage temperature from -40°C to 85°C.

items.description: This is an optimized ABLS Switched Mode Power Supply (SMPS) that provides DC voltage. Rated input voltage from 100 V to 240 V AC and 140 V to 340 V DC, rated output current of 5 A at 24 V DC and rated output power of 120 W. Suitable for DC power supply required in areas such as transportation, packaging, management, food processing, mining, oil and gas and water supply. Mounted on a DIN rail or fixed with screws. Width 40 mm, height 123.6 mm, depth 117.6 mm. Provides protection against overloads and short circuits with automatic restart after removal of the source of overload/short circuit. Weight 0.550 kg. Complies with standards EN62368-1, ENIEC61010-1/2-201, ENIEC61204-3, EN61000-6-1/2/3/4, EN61000-3-2-3, UL62368-1, UL61010-2-201/-1-201, CSAC22. 2No62368-1/No61010-2-201/No61010-1 and certified by CE, CUL, RCM, CBscheme. For its protection, it is recommended to use Acti9 iC60 miniature switches. Protection type - 16A, curve C or 13A. There is an LED on the front panel to indicate the presence of DC output voltage, as well as a QR code to access the latest technical documentation. It is installed both in cabinets and on industrial panels, fixing on a DIN rail. Designed for simple machines, modular power supplies are primarily valued for their extreme compactness.
